          <param name="script.content"><![CDATA[echo "hello"

echo "filecontents" > Outputs.zip

exit 1]]></param>
          <param name="teamcity.step.mode" value="default" />
          <param name="use.custom.script" value="true" />
        </parameters>
      </runner>
    </build-runners>
    <vcs-settings />
    <requirements />
    <build-triggers />
    <cleanup />
  </settings>
</build-type>
